headline: 5 Insightful Analyst Questions From Paycom’s Q3 Earnings Call
summary: Paycom’s third quarter results were met with a significant negative market reaction, as investors digested both the company’s in-line revenue performance and a slight miss on non-GAAP earnings per share.
